  <lyrics>[V1]
 Munat jilata cuttanjjamay jucha lurañata;
 Sitejj suyáta ucapachajj jiwañaw catjátam;
 Jichpachay Diosar maqhatanjjam,
 Salvación utjquipan.
 
[C]
 Kollan Awquimajj suyasctam,
 Jach'a munasifiapanipi,
 Cusisitaw jumarojja catokasjjátamjja. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Munat jilata arsusjjamay take juchanaca;
 lyawsamay Tatit Cristoru. perdón jicjjatátaw;
 Llamp'u chuymampiy mayisimjja
 Munasir Awquimar.
 
[V3]
 Tatit Cristojj janc'aw jutjjani acá orakeru;
 Khespiyat jakenacarojja irpasjjestaniwa;
 Janc'aquiy jumajj Cristor jutjjam.
 Jupamp sarjjañatac.
 
</lyrics></song>